<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TMaL13">
<l>eṟiyunīr veṟikoḷ vēlai mānilat tuyirka ḷellām</l>
<l>veṟikoḷpūn tuḷava mālai viṇṇavar kōṉai yētta</l>
<l>aṟivilā maṉita rellā maraṅkameṉ ṟaḻaippa rākiṟ</l>
<l>poṟiyilvāḻ naraka mellām pulleḻun toḻiyu maṉṟē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The living beings on the big earth [surrounded by] the fragrant ocean with splashing water</l>
<l>praise the King of celestials [who wears] pretty, fragrant tulasi garlands.</l>
<l>[When such is the case] if all the humans devoid of knowledge</l>
<l>would [only] call out saying ‘Raṅgam!,’</l>
<l>all the hells that live in the sense organs</l>
<l>will be destroyed with grass growing [on them], will they not?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
